        Probate and the Deceased Estate Sale Timeline in Brisbane
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        How long does probate take in Queensland, and what does it mean for selling a deceased estate property? A clear timeline from death to settlement, including what causes delays and what executors need to know.
      </p>
